    <td colspan="3" width="585"><p align="center">
    <font color="#9f3215" face="verdana" size="2">The regular ol' kobold.  This is the foot soldier of the whole bunch, you might also say that they're the average citizen of the Kobold civilization.  They serve no purpose whatsoever except to annoy you, the adventurer.  They have no special abilities and are found in a few small camps here and there.</font></td>
