		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			The level posted here is wrong, highest ive ever seen was a lvl 7 shaman and they go low enough that my level 3 bard was taking some down that had an even fight con. I would say the majority of them are 3-6 at the most, the shamans are usualy 4-7 and sometimes spawn in the same spots as the regular kobs.  Also the shamans are bugged, when they attack they say &quot;Orc Stomp, Orc Kill, Orc spill your blood&quot; or something to that affect which i found a little funny.
			</font>
	
		</td>
	</tr>
	
